  Alstom SA ,  Drax Group Plc  and
National Grid Plc are seeking European Union funding for a new
U.K. carbon capture and storage demonstration project in Selby,
North Yorkshire, Alstom said today in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
